    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Layout: 13 long lines in cloudbands; border-ruled.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Script: Written in naskh in black ink; pointed, vocalized.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Decoration: Textblock border-ruled in gold and double blue with the text on cloudbands throughout. Headpiece in blue and gold on the first opening with textblock frame of blue line designs (f. 1v). Page-opening frame of colored (blue and red) and gold leaves on first and last opening (f. 1v-2r, 241v-242r). Gold foliate page-opening frame on three sides throughout; the frame has been partially or fully trimmed on pages near the beginning. Rubrications in blue and red.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
